{"uuid":"recommended208346","createDate":1760410023353,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"208346\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:23:08\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2019-09-10\",\"gameName\":\"Train Simulator: Class 158 DMU Add-On\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/208346\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/208346/\",\"playTime\":\"0.0\",\"updateTime\":\"2019-09-10\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"0.0\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/208346\"}","type":"steamReview","title":"评测 > Train Simulator: Class 158 DMU Add-On","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n 模拟火车：Class 158 DMU柴油机车组\n <br>\n 包含了Class158 DMU和相关涂装~但是没有职业任务~\n <br>\n 其实还有另外一个DLC包含了Class158~但是那个DLC应该只包含ATW的1个涂装\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/376941/Train_Simulator_Arriva_Trains_Wales_DMU_Pack_AddOn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/376941/Train_Simulator_Arriva_Trains_Wales_DMU_Pack_AddOn/</a>\n <br>\n 而这个DLC会补齐剩下5个涂装~至于机车~emm~看上去重复了~\n <br>\n <br>\n 职业任务是ATW的DLC中的~这个DLC的158只有快速任务的独立机车、涂装、客运车厢~\n <br>\n <br>\n 双音喇叭、车内灯光、仪表灯光、车灯开关都模拟到了~\n <br>\n 涂装也很漂亮、客运车厢也有客人了~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1859452129\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1859452129</a>\n <br>\n <br>\n 不过这车的视野真不怎么样~右边完全挡住了~只能看到左边和前方的视线~\n <br>\n （车头中间还有个过道~这设计简直直接当客运车厢用咯~~）\n <br>\n 驾驶室顶部标示了最高时速为90英里/小时~但是我可以开到100mph~\n <br>\n 一直到时速表的尽头~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1859452341\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_2\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1859452341</a>\n <br>\n 这车加速和刹车都不怎么好~而且加速的时候偶尔还有诡异的共振声~\n <br>\n <br>\n 我一直以为这车就是个地铁车~结果其实每个站点距离还是很长的~\n <br>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ReviewEdit\" style=\"display: none\">\n <textarea id=\"ReviewEdit